Alto kɛna [[minziiki]] wonuu. Kɩwɛ minziiki wondu hɔʋ taa. Ɛkɛ minziiki wonuu ŋgʋ palʋkʋ nɛ nimee yɔ. Ɛwɛtʋ taa paza pɩkpaɣ wonuu ŋgʋ paya kʋkʋ size vɩɔlɔɔ yɔ.

Ɛlɛ, ɛ-palaɣ pɩkɩlɩ, nɛ ɛwɛ ɖɔɖɔ kpɛzɛlɛɛɛ pɩkɩlɩ, nɛ pɩtɛ ɛlɩ muduleee ɛnɩɣʋ taa pila kagbanzɩ taa (quinte). Ki-wiluu lɛɛzʋʋ sakɩyɛ taa talɩɣ ɛzɩ 128 Hz pɩsɩna 2600 Hz mbʋ yɔ.

Katɔrɩ nimaa n̄ɩŋgʋ taa lɛ, ɖɩnaɣ (2 Vɩɔlɔɔ yaa alto yaa vɩɔlɔsɛlɩ). Alto wiluu wɛ ɖɔɖɔ kɛɛkɛ ɛzɩ abalʋ kɩlɩm nɔɔ wiluu wɛʋ yɔ, kɛ wiliŋ tɩŋɛ taa (sɔpranɔ, yaa alto, yaa abalʋ kɩlɩm nɔɔ wiluu, nɛ wiluu hɛɛɛ ŋga).

[[File:Frantz Loriot 02.JPG|thumb|Frantz Loriot 02]]

E-loya ɖasam loniye wala siŋŋ. Ɖooo pɩɩkpaɣʋ nɛ ɖaɣnʋʋ lʋlʋʋ lʋbɩyɛ lɩmaɣzɩyɛ wayɩ yɔ nɛ pɩkɔ pɩsɩna lɛɛlɛyɔ.

Soo n̄ɩɣʋ kʋnɛ, kʋ-tʋma sʋsɔna kpaɣna ɖooo kpaɖʋ 18 ŋgʋ taa nɛ Georg Philipp Telemann tɛ konserto maʋ yɔ. Ɖɩnaɣ ɖɔɖɔ Symphonie concertante kɛ vɩɔlɔ nɛ alto kɛ [[Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart|Mozart]] hɩɖɛ taa,nɛ Stamitz nɛ Hoffmeister nɛ pɩtasɩna Rolla ɖɔɖɔ pa-tʋma taa.

Kpaɖʋ 20 taa lɛ, minziiki wondu luɖa sakɩyɛ ka-mawa ɖɔɖɔ konserto waa kɛ alto hɔɔlʋʋ taa. Ɛyaa panɛ ɖɔɖɔ : Béla Bartók, nɛ Paul Hindemith,nɛ pɩtasɩna William Walton.

Ɖɩɖɔkɩ size alto kɛ minziiki wonuu ŋgʋ kʋwɛ ɖɔɖɔ camɩyɛ kaŋ kɛ soo n̄ɩyɩŋ ɖɩjaɣyɛ loya ɖasam loniye taa yɔ.

Nɛ ɖɔɖɔ siŋŋ lɛ, alto kɛ minziiki ɖandɛ n̄ɩŋʋ.

